{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ca055694a6","title":"到锦州前线指挥作战应保障安全","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3845dd8922","index":0,"year":1948,"month":10,"day":6,"articleId":"ca055694a6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5bb489f7c3","type":"paragraph","text":"到锦州前线指挥作战应保障安全“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ca055694a6"},{"id":"ad5062c6d6","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年10月6日）林、罗、刘：四日九时电器。（一）你们到锦州附近指挥甚好。但你们不应距城太近，应在距城较远之处以电话能联络各城兵团即妥，务求保障安全。另设攻城直接指挥所，委托适当人员，乘承你们意台，追近城量指挥（亦不要太近）。（二）国民党统治机构全般乱，一切战场处于被动，士气一般下降，望鼓励全军将士奋勇杀敌，争取大胜。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ca055694a6"},{"id":"5a3f025199","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ca055694a6"},{"id":"ee9aeaf50a","type":"paragraph","text":"六日二时[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给东北野战军司令员林、政治委员罗荣植和参谋长刘亚楼的电报[2]指1948年10月4日9时林息、罗荣植和刘亚给中共中央军委并继续前进到锦州附近指择，我框任攻后续部队，正向锦州前进中，约五田后可到齐。”","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ca055694a6"}],"page":{"id":"9c1be79d86","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ca055694a6","start":530,"end":530}}}},"__N_SSG":true}